{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad apſlehpehs Dahwids\nLankâ/ un kad tas jauns Meh-\nnes bija/ tad apſehdehs tas Keh-\nninsch Maisti ehſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu tas Kehninsch bij\napſehdees fawa Weetâ/ to Brih-\ndi lihds ka zittkahrt pee Seenas/\ntad zehlehs Jonatans/ un Abners\naptehdahs fahnis Saulu/ bet\nDahwida Weeta palikke tukſcha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Sauls ne runnaja\ntai Deenaâ ne neeka/ jo wiꞥſch\ndohmoja/ tam irr kas notizzis/ ka\ntas schkihts ne irr/ wiꞥſch ne\nbuhs schkihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Rihta Deenaâ/ kaſ\nta jauna Mehnes ohtra bija/ pa-\nlikke Dahwida Weeta atkat tuḵ-\nfcha/ tad fazzija Sauls us fawu\nDehlu Jonatann: Rapehz ne irr\ntas Dehls Isaja/ nedg wakkar\nnedg schodeen pee Galda nahzis?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Jonatans\nSaulam: Dahwidsluhdse mann\ntik mihti/ ka tas warretu us Bet-\nlemi ect/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fazzija: Atlaid mann/\nluhdsams/ jo muhsu Raddam irr\nweens Uppurs tä Pilsfahta/ un\nmans Brahtis irr man pats to\npaweblejs: Nu tad/ ja es Scheh-\nlastibu efmu atraddis tawäs Az-\nzis/ tad dohd man luhdsanis\nWaltu/ ka es sawus Brahtus\nwarru apluhkoht/ tadeht wiꞥſch\nne irr nahzis pee ta Kehnina\nGalda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad apſkaitahs Sauls\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "prett Jonatann/ un fazzija us to\nTu neklausigs Blehdneeks/ w-\nes ne finnu/ ka tu to Dehlu Is-\nja effi isredsejs tew par Kannu\nun tawai netiklai Mahtei pa\nKannu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo zik igi tas Dehls Is-\nja wirs Semmes dshwohs/ n-\ntapsi tu nedg tawa Walſtiva ap-\nstiprinata. Tad nu notuhrt/ u-\ndabbu man winnu tchurp/\nwinnam buhs mirt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Jonatan-\nfawam Tehwan Saulam/ n-\nfazzija us to: Rapehz buhs tan-\nmirt/ ko irr wiꞥſch darrijs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad schahwe Sauls t-\nSchekhpu pehz winna/ ka win-\nto nodurtu. Tad famantija Jo-\nnatans/ ka no winna Tehwa tit-\nri bijapremts/ Dahwidu nokau-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jonatans zehlehs n-\nta Galda ar Dufinahm/ un n-\nehde ohtra jauna Mehnes Deen-\nne neeka/ jo winnam bij Behda-\npahr Dahwidu/ tapehz ka win-\nTehws to bij atmettis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Rihta isgahje Jon-\ntans Lankâ/ us to Laiku/ ka-\nDahwidam bij noliktâ/ un ween-\nmasajs Puifs bija ar win-\nlihds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija ustaw-\nPuiti: Tezz/ metke jelle tah-\nBultas/ ko es schauschu. Tad tez-\nzeja tas Puifs/ un tas fchahw-\nweenu Bultu pahri pahr winnu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tas Puifsus t-\nBultas Weetu nahze/ ko Jona-\nnatan\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
